I'm yesterday.

291
00:39:44,375 --> 00:39:47,621
You've been listening to our cuckoo.

292
00:39:47,981 --> 00:39:53,472
- He's not so cuckoo.
- You can tell the time by him.

293
00:40:09,813 --> 00:40:12,566
