347
00:47:45,793 --> 00:47:47,635
I don't know.

348
00:47:48,168 --> 00:47:49,681
You don't know?!

349
00:47:51,265 --> 00:47:54,541
If we weren't in eclipse,
we could call Central.

350
00:47:54,713 --> 00:47:57,976
And if we were chickens,
we could lay eggs.

351
00:47:57,977 --> 00:48:01,676
