509
01:17:28,846 --> 01:17:31,280
Now, this way, please.

510
01:17:38,353 --> 01:17:39,627
Adam!

511
01:17:48,228 --> 01:17:52,256
When I heard your voice,
I thought I was going mad.

512
01:17:54,207 --> 01:17:56,268
Oh, Alex.

513
01:17:57,847 --> 01:18:00,313
Hurry along, please.

514
01:18:03,667 --> 01:18:06,448
